title: My Sally in dream
description:
few days ago. i had a dream... i was wandering in a magical forest.... it's so beautiful and fantasy....and...all of a sudden...i hear something very softly ....sound like someone is calling....

than....i find out there's a Elf girl sitting under the tree...

she give me a innocent face...and her eyes like two stars in the dark sky.....

OH....MY....
it's Sally Acorn!!


she said to me.... '' who ever you are....if you save me...i will give you anything....."
i look at her....find out she was tied by chain


who did this?


but there is no time to find out. so i touch the chain..and suddenly.the chain untied! than she stand up and thank me. she has a most wonderful smile ever....^///^


i don't quit remember what happen next. but it is such a beautiful dream. so i drew this picture. like a image....and...sigh.....i must said i am not good at drewing....(there are so many art genius here....)or sally should more beautiful and cuter than this...sorry...

summer vacation is over....so sad...i 'm went back to school few days ago....and i have to study hard!so i can get to a nice college. so....won't have too much time show up on DA. sorry about that......

May Lord bless Sally acorn and bless all the student. may you wish come ture!

sign AVCHonline
